title: Palmeiras in the top four (CONMEBOL - Confederación Sudamericana de Fútbol)
text: ( Source : CONMEBOL - Confederación Sudamericana de Fútbol ) On Saturday Palmeiras won 3-1 against Avaí to jump to fourth place in the standins, which would give the club a ticket to the Copa Libertadores . ​ Gabriel Jesús (17), Jonathan
